title: Superbowl Halftime Speech
description:
Written by Zack Phillips
Starring Jonathan Marballi, Dan Hodapp, Kerry O'Brien, Langan Kingsley

Directed by Jim Santangeli

From Maude Night at the Upright Citizens Brigade Theatre, February 3, 2014.

Filmed by Matthew Alston and Curtis Raye.
Edited by Curtis Raye.
